name: FFGOnlineSessionSettings
comment:
using the Unreal Reflection system, the keys names used to propagate the settings is
the variable name, then the variables is converted to strings and back.

properties.name: HostId
properties.comment: IMPORTANT: Don't rename this! This is parsed in engine code

properties.name: NumConnectedPlayers
properties.comment: Number of players currently connected to the game

properties.name: PlayDuration
properties.comment: For how long has the game been played in seconds

properties.name: BuildVersion
properties.comment: The build version on the form ++FactoryGame+Main-4.20-CL-123456

properties.name: SessionName
properties.comment: Name of the session, same as the name exposed in the Save/Load menus
